{
  "stem": "26672.4",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And we got pictures taken with him in [NON-ENGLISH] Park, which doesn't exist now.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And what was [NON-ENGLISH] doing out there?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "[NON-ENGLISH] also-- I don't know how he came into-- because he was with the Anglo-Saxons as a volunteer.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I don't know how he came to our camp.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "He must have been-- but before that, it's a very important little story I forgot.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "We were in one camp.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And in those days, as you arrived from the boats, [?",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Latrun ?], a very notorious place-- most strategic points, we had police stations were built along citadels in the strategic areas.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "[?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Latrun ?] was up on the hill.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "[INAUDIBLE] almost take, in those days, people from the boat without any experience, and sent into [?",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "Latrun ?].",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And many, many got killed.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "There were-- we were in one camp, [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And we had-- there was an order to assemble.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And we were going to be shipped to [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "Whether it was a [INAUDIBLE], or what, I can't remember.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And [NON-ENGLISH] and I looked at each other.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And we said-- it was already known then it was an infamous place, notorious.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And we looked at each other.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And we said, it's not for us.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "So we're trying to find how to get out of it.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "And we decided we were going to hide.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "It's not very nice of us, after we came to fight in the army.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "I don't know whether it flashed through that I just try and stay alive or what, I didn't know.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "But anyway, we decided we were not going to turn up.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "And we didn't.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "The camp was taken out on-- on-- on wagons, transporters, transporters, army transporters, to [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "And we managed to not turn up.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "After a while, we were walking through the camp.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
